Three arrested in Midcoast bank fraud attempts

Three people from New York were arrested after police say they attempted to withdraw thousands using fraudulent identification at Midcoast banks.

![](https://media.newscentermaine.com/assets/NCM/images/df85b8b4-8b2f-4ee6-af0e-3e35e7f3939c/df85b8b4-8b2f-4ee6-af0e-3e35e7f3939c_16x9.jpg) ![](https://media.newscentermaine.com/assets/NCM/images/df85b8b4-8b2f-4ee6-af0e-3e35e7f3939c/df85b8b4-8b2f-4ee6-af0e-3e35e7f3939c_750x422.jpg)

Credit: NCM

